title: Kendall Jenner and A$AP Rocky Were Seen Entering the Same Hotel in Milan
text:
It was only a matter of time until fashion's It couple made a high-profile appearance during fashion month. As Milan Fashion Week kicked into full gear, Kendall Jenner and her rumored boyfriend A$AP Rocky were spotted together for a night out—or in, rather. The 21-year-old model and 28-year-old rapper were seen entering a hotel together in the Italian city last night. Jenner bundled up in an army-green jacket, leather pants and ankle boots; while Rocky layered a camel coat over a Gucci hoodie, cream-colored trousers and Reebok sneakers.
